Class
Class is a blueprint

Object
Object is instances of class


Methods Vs Functions
Methods: That functions inside the class/constructor
Functions: That are outside of the class
Ex: 
L=[1,2,3,4]
len(L) -> function because it is not built in List class
L.append(5) ->method because it belongs to List


